Class TemperatureGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • logic.TemperatureGenerator

  • public class TemperatureGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    TemperatureGenerator class is used to generate annual data regarding air and underground temperatures as well as some other temperature statistics.
